  "title": "Waste Sorter needed at Sungei Kadut",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p>· Identify and sort collected waste Deposit recyclable waste on conveyor belts as directed</p>\n<p>· Ensure safety measures are adhered to during waste sorting operations</p>\n<p>· Handle tools and equipment</p>\n<p>· Ensure the appropriate tools and equipment are in working condition</p>\n<p>· Report equipment faults to the supervisor Ensure tools and equipment are replenished timely, reinstated and maintained Manage incidents</p>\n<p>· Report operational abnormalities to the appropriate person</p>\n<p>· Respond to incidents and emergencies as directed</p>\n<p>· Any other tasks appointed by your immediate supervisor.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<p>· Physically fit and attentive</p>\n<p>· Able stand over a period of time while performing primary role of waste sorting</p>",
